# Open Source Licenses

The licenses of lisplens itself (MPL-2.0) and of every Rust dependency bundled into
the release binary, so a binary-only distribution carries the notices those licenses
require. Dev-only crates (test/build tooling, never shipped) are excluded.

_Generated by `cargo about generate about.hbs -o THIRD-PARTY-LICENSES.md`; do not
edit by hand. Entries are grouped by license text — each distinct license body
appears once, with the list of crates that use it._

